{"tid":854940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"要一個你愛既人 定係 一個愛你既人？","createTime":"2018-10-09T17:05:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T00:19:29.000Z","uid":181017,"like":128,"dislike":160,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7f4a6660553d234ddd2f9a6bedb07ef88f8a8248","tid":854940,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"通常會好理智咁講：梗係要個愛自己既人。<br />\n<br />\n但當你同時遇到依兩個人，你個心總會話你知，你想揀一個自己愛既人。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話點解唔揀個，你愛佢佢又愛你既人，就算大家都愛大家，都總會有方愛多啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果同時出現 一個愛你既既人 同 一個你愛既人<br />\n你點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛你既人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你愛既人<br />\n<br />\n分享下點解咁揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c9c135521035973c28339ac2b8349e2a17e5e5","tid":854940,"uid":74277,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:07:39.000Z","msg":"俾公認女神既女仔鍾意過 事實未必如理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f064d41ea7e3105eaa2d69deb6aa1eaee4b4f71","tid":854940,"uid":115441,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"因為你愛既人通常唔愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb319cc8aef243f807e5922ea3be9623d9f3bd1","tid":854940,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:09:18.000Z","msg":"糞得好無煩惱"},{"pid":"637441e3cdadec171a691a4a03bb4fd8ef39ec45","tid":854940,"uid":199947,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"自己唔愛其實好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a05860abf0f4b42cdd2a