Z","msg":"提子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac3d0619ebb372e536147c664f6f898958813a8","tid":854940,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91dcc3d22469ab2ca3c976a5fd13d839f907aeb3","tid":854940,"uid":140018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"人付出得多先會珍惜，所以一定會揀自己愛既人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"付出梗知陣，比人當狗咁撚架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c95382c6f5083b5504663720e1a643dce5e289","tid":854940,"uid":103321,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"揀個愛我而我唔愛佢嘅人其實冇意思，<br />\n個心始終會喺我愛嘅人度，<br />\n就算我愛嘅人唔愛自己甚至對自己差都好，<br />\n都會覺得自己所有付出都係值得。<br />\n揀個愛我嘅人只係自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S.試過"},{"pid":"c36a864ed874c0664fad6bbc4de354c480cd1006","tid":854940,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac3d0619ebb372e536147c664f6f898958813a8","tid":854940,"uid":181017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91dcc3d22469ab2ca3c976a5fd13d839f907aeb3","tid":854940,"uid":140018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:19:34.000Z","msg":"人付出得多先會珍惜，所以一定會揀自己愛既人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:54:35.000Z","msg":"付出梗知陣，比人當狗咁撚架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"個陣"},{"pid":"48b27a49c545da32ffea94f821db2aed4dc604ef","tid":854940,"uid":181017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23c95382c6f5083b5504663720e1a643dce5e289","tid":854940,"uid":103321,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"揀個愛我而我唔愛佢嘅人其實冇意思，<br />\n個心始終會喺我愛嘅人度，<br />\n就算我愛嘅人唔愛自己甚至對自己差都好，<br />\n都會覺得自己所有付出都係值得。<br />\n揀個愛我嘅人只係自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nP.S.試過"},"citedBy":1,"reply